'''1905年大西洋飓风季'''确定存在五个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，其中两个曾[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]美国。第一个天气系统最初于9月6日在[[向风群岛|向风群岛]]附近出现，第四号热带风暴于10月11日在[[纽芬兰与拉布拉多|纽芬兰与拉布拉多]]较远处海域转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，都在[[大西洋|大西洋盆地]]每年绝大多数热带天气活动的时间范围内。10月5至10日间，第四和第五个热带气旋曾同时存在。

全季五个热带气旋中只有第四个达到飓风强度，是[[1890年大西洋飓风季|1890年]]后最少的一年。不过，这场飓风的[[最大持续风速|最高风速]]达每小时195公里，不但是本季最强风暴，而且达到现代[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的三级飓风标准{{#tag:ref|[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]于1971年面世<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | author = Jack Williams | title = Hurricane scale invented to communicate storm danger | publisher = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2005-05-17 | accessdate = 2013-08-04 | url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160324154907/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/weather/hurricane/whscale.htm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-24 }}</ref>，再对[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]大西洋飓风数据库的所有风暴追溯分级<ref>{{cite report | publisher = Hurricane Research Division | title = Chronological List of All Continental United States Hurricanes: 1851-2012 | date = 2013-06 | accessdate = 2016-11-10 | archivedate = 2016-05-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160503012801/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/All_U.S._Hurricanes.html }}</ref>。|group="注"}}，属[[热带气旋等级|大型飓风]]。<ref name="ACE" />气旋产生的疯狗浪导致“坎帕尼亚号”汽船至少六人遇难。此外，本季首场风暴还在[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]致使一艘[[双桅纵帆船|双桅纵帆船]]沉没，船上两人丧生。

这年飓风季的低迷活跃程度还经累积[[气旋能量指数|气旋能量指数]]反映出来，数值仅28，是[[1864年大西洋飓风季|1864年]]后新低<ref>{{cite report | author = Hurricane Research Division | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2011-03 | title = Atlantic basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | accessdate = 2016-03-04 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040342/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/Comparison_of_Original_and_Revised_HURDAT_mar11.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。大致来说，气旋能量指数通过飓风强度和持续时间计算，强度越高、持续时间越长的风暴，其指数也相应越高。只有在热带天气系统风速达到或超过每小时63公里（34[[节_(单位)|节]]）或热带风暴强度时才会计算该指数，并纳入全面的气象公告，并且[[亚热带气旋|亚热带气旋]]的指数不会计入累积数值。<ref>{{cite web |author=David Levinson |date=2008-08-20 |title=2005 Atlantic Ocean Tropical Cyclones |publisher=National Climatic Data Center |archiveurl=https://archive.li/20131105020723/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html |archivedate=2013-11-05 |deadurl=no |accessdate=2014-04-01 |url=http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/oa/climate/research/2005/2005-atlantic-trop-cyclones.html }}</ref><ref name="ACE">{{cite report | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | title = Atlantic Basin Comparison of Original and Revised HURDAT | date = 2014-02 | work = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-12-09 | location = Miami, Florida | archivedate = 2016-04-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160425073956/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/comparison_table.html | deadurl = no }}</ref>
