9月6日，[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]以东海域出现本季首场热带风暴<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite web | author = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | author2 = Hurricane Research Division | title = Atlantic hurricane best track (HURDAT version 2) | accessdate = 2016-11-01 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2016-07-06 | archivedate = 2016-10-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161004150702/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/hurdat/hurdat2-1851-2015-070616.txt | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | deadurl = no }}</ref>。气旋规模很小，于9月7日清晨快速经过[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]南部<ref name="MWR">{{cite report | author = Cleveland Abbe | author2 = Frank Owen Stettson | last-author-amp = yes | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration; Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | work = [[美国国家气象局|United States Weather Bureau]] | year = 1906 | accessdate = 2016-12-09 | location = Miami, Florida | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303214553/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1905.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1905.pdf | title = Monthly Weather Review for 1905 | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | date =  }}</ref>。次日，风暴强度下滑至热带低气压标准，之后被规模更大但强度不及的天气系统吸收<ref name="HURDAT" /><ref name="MWR" />。从[[布里奇敦|布里奇敦]]出发前往[[苏利南|苏利南]]的一艘[[双桅纵帆船|双桅纵帆船]]在离港次日就遇上恶劣海况，不得不返航。但船还是撞上码头并沉没，船长及另一名船员被卷走后溺毙。<ref name="MWR" />
